name: MY DATE IN LA TOKENÍA.
description:
This work is part of the First Collective Exhibition of La Tokenía.

La Tokenía is a place where you can go to have a drink, listen to a tasty merengue and talk about the latest news from the nft world with artists and entities of Venezuelan origin.

This is my vision of that mysterious place that I am a part of.

A Milestone begins.

Original Art and Animation by Flores Solano
2021
